<body class = dosdontssection>
  <div class= div1> 
<h1 class = header1> What to do to prepare for the process of taking out a loan: </h1> 
<br>

<ul class = dosList>
  <li>Save money</li>
  <li>Have good credit</li>
  <li>Pay bills on time</li>
  <li> Plan out what the loan is being used for</li> 
  <li>Have a stable job</li>
  <li>Make sure you know you can pay the loan back</li>
  <li>Figure out how you will be paying the loan back</li>
  <li>Make sure you understand how the loan works (any interest rates? Is there different bank locations that meet your standard of taking a loan out?)</li>
  <li>Make sure you understand the process</li>
  <li>Make sure to ask questions about anything you are still confused about</li>
</ul>  


</div> 

<div class= div2>
<h1 class = header1> What to avoid when in the process of taking out a loan:</h1> 
<br>

<ul class= dontsList>
  <li>Don't have bad credit </li>
  <li>Don't have an unstable job</li>
  <li>Don't be paying bills late</li>
  <li> Don't take out a loan without having a plan with the loan </li> 
  <li>Don't take out a loan without knowing how you will pay it back</li>
  <li>Don't take out a loan without knowing the process of taking out a loan </li>
  <li>Don't hesitate to ask questions</li>
</ul> 
  

  </div> 
